dc_title_s: Shinsen jissoku Tōkyō zu: zen Nagamatsu Sakunosuke.
dc_description_s: Cover title. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the right. Relief shown by hachures. Shows views of tourist attractions. Includes address chart and legend. 1 map: col.; 46 x 62 cm.,folded in cover 18 x 10 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
